每个车站都配备了监控摄像、金属探测仪、行李安检设备，可谓是该市最安全的交通方式。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_kolkata-metro-to-install-x-ray-baggage-scanners_1749283|title=Kolkata metro to install x-ray baggage scanners|work=Daily News and Analysis|date=2012-10-05|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-date=2012-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019032348/http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_kolkata-metro-to-install-x-ray-baggage-scanners_1749283|dead-url=no}}</ref>

